data.description: Welcome Home! This 4 bedroom/2.5 bath home offers so much space for your family and entertaining needs! The bedrooms are all spacious with tons of storage. Master bedroom is huge with closets and an en-suite full bathroom. Many updates to the home include, hot water tank 2022, Basement waterproofing with sump pump 2023, new flooring on main floor 2021, finished basement 2023, kitchen plumbing 2023, New dryer 2023 and refrigerator 2023. Eat in kitchen, formal dining room, additional living space with deck access currently being used as an office. Finished basement/rec room with a nice 1/2 bath. There is a 2 car garage and a huge yard with a deck for family fun! This beautiful home is located within a few minutes of the highway, restaurants and shopping. Move in ready, so don't miss your opportunity to check all your boxes on your Wishlist. This is HOME!
